title: Hour 3 - Adrian Wojnarowski and Dana White (06-04-20)

description:
Adrian Wojnarowski breaks down the future of the NBA and how they will make it work in Orlando. Dana White talks to Dan about the upcoming event and he tells Dan the Fight Island is a reality and will be happening sooner than later.
